###Features

All accounts are based on a cpanel CloudLinux server with PHP Selector available. 

We also have installatron for automated app/software installation. 

A number of highly requested modules such as ModPageSpeed are also enabled.

###DDoS Protection:

DDoS Protection is provided by NTT.

###Network:

You can test our network using our [London LookingGlass instance](http://lg-ldn-uk.quadhost.net).

###Transparency:

We offer a real time status page showing current system load and resource utilisation on our website. We also have 3rd party independent monitoring recorded via StatusCake.

